Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.37,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仰望天空 广阔梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:08.31,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}打开未来的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:15.31,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.62,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明朗的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:30.08,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}打开窗便有阳光洒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.62,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}微风拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:36.56,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}拭去昨日的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.05,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}寂寞之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.82,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}总是寻找着看不见的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.20,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不知它近在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:52.45,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}依然不断追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.83,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}（you are the shining star）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:57.34,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}仰望天空 广阔梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.28,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}打开未来的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:07.91,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.42,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}星空闪烁的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.45,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不计其数的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:21.78,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}如今依然等待着你去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:26.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}所以迈步前进吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN2-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:29.97,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.65,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:49.28,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:53.46,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:57.28,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:01.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:04.08,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:08.88,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:12.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:19.24,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:21.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:22.88,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:27.07,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:31.69,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.86,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:38.62,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:42.99,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.80,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.91,0:23:47.19,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:50.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:55.31,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
