Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位住宿生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假最后的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宿舍主办的烧烤派对之夜现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此就这么几个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还没从老家回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假还留在宿舍的人才不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的南方小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假不在这里度过不是太可惜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来本田学长在宿舍里面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙打工时受到的心灵创伤还没痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是打零工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要走上现实社会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有超乎想象的惊喜在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为估计人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的大换血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 未经许可不要擅自行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚本来打算好好享受宁静的暑假结尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个活动本来是宿舍代代相传
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有住宿生参加的传统…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏打放这里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火热的夏天还没结束呢
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:40.99,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(594,326)\be1}（现在正在举行“真心话”烟花大会）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 其实期末考试时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里响起的奇怪雷声是我的肚子在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮（注：原文玉屋，放烟花时表示赞赏）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 其实之前给拓人君做便当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对着刚炸好的炸土豆饼花了5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入lovelove念力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我经常让女仆帮我冲背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我初吻的对象是我养的猫雷奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不能吃青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哑炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 红绪穿泳装翻单杠100次是我偷拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃呃 那个…以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不对不对 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是拓人君输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子和袜子都脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是没什么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌 好像很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点脱啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们似乎在做很有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看板郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是脱衣舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这位似乎也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跑出来还真厚脸皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.24,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(530,322)\be1}（很危险 玩烟花的人千万不要模仿）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哉 给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天真火热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是小火灾就了事已经算万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志同学的房间被烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要考虑一下住宿才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以寄宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢了须方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都烧完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假最后的活动就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把换洗衣服放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了呢 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 要我帮您冲背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 总之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好把这个放口袋里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的表？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服和课本总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的事明天再想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我也没怎么消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 毕竟是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是须方君以前用过的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是须方小时候画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那涂鸦是我画的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常来这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 给你看样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候经常扮偶像玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 班长丹治惠都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人一起转进我们班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富煌和慧窗华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们班很有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给学长做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是奖励做菜的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是奖励吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的暑假结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的新学期就开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子选定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的火灾 够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩了下火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身家当都化成灰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话真是陷入绝境了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得找打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且赖在须方家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩火怎么不跟我玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好像会严重烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我在须方家看到相册了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你以前跟和子扮偶像组合？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是陈年往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片和现在的印象差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可和子现在还说要当歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.57,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}等待着朝霞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:29.04,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不安的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.38,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寻回的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.71,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即便是无心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.13,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}秋色的风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.77,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用老成的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.26,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将逝去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.76,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}教给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:50.03,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}来来往往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.07,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}思考烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:12:00.84,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那唯一的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:06.53,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寻找着 一触即破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.45,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}等待着结局 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:13.20,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}令人忧伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.17,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}逼近心底的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.30,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}破坏中开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.17,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}诞生的生命 即使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.96,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.73,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心中却已接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:36.94,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}紧闭的眼眸 已彼此相系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.91,INCN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 现实社会上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有超乎想象的惊喜在等待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给店里帮忙又在玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样每天跳得这么兴高采烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己是偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是从今天开始在我们家打工的津名志君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话招来当女婿也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent（窗）还在搁浅中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先导出你和当前奥利哈康波动周期顶点的计算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也需要几天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且选择复原的素体需要总会的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为可以更轻松地复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩多少次就能玩多少次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了第四阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就不需要这些复杂的机械界面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以凭驭星者的意志随意复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的阶段复原可是有生命危险的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说失败可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启程之日到来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这些家伙驾着素体跑出零时空间肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真的会有危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也变成无聊人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能早点玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有玩具好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拥有真正印记的驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使素体坏了应该也可以用第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎也很有趣
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公演快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了水野 还得招收新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说这是柔软体操
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如当成宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们还有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要好的样子真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不会告诉任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是戏剧部的粉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的粉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是2班的转校生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富煌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧窗华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对戏剧部没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1班的班长 丹治惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们玩个开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有社团活动的日子就不要练剑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能一招打倒我就停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一脸不满的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换房租不收你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点抛弃那种天真的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用木刀练习本身就很天真了 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好罢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 房东
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 食客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent 第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种刀法…是拓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这黑暗是窗之星的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来全都是我窗之星的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要打到自己人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pinch吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就让它结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中 你只能识别出自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别出自己就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你下手轻一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.76,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(564,426)\be1}（很危险 使用第一阶段的人千万不要模仿）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方 真不可小视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 只不过是自己怕死才这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 真是毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种性格为什么还会受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君其实很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 倒是让我白吃白住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我要是扮偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是很开心地夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 班长也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长现在也对须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让逆日死之巫女做的工作是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 并不是我让她去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作辛苦了 逆日死大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一阵子都没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今晚又陷入了沉眠之底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日是和子的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要亲手做料理庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 当我们来到城里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团的魔掌却逐渐逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的周日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 已经在闪耀
